{"type": "article", "id": 29435, "title": "白熊杯盖", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-11T23:01:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160711212235PWX1QImulDKMHzga.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>等待茶叶泡开的时间有了白熊的陪伴不会再觉得无聊了。这个纯白的陶瓷杯盖由日本工作室 <a href=\"http://necktie.tokyo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NECKTIE</a> 设计，全部在以制作陶器为名的长崎县波佐见町由当地工匠手工烧制，陶瓷的加工和涂装则在东京的工厂进行。杯盖上的白熊举着一根竿子，泡茶时将茶叶袋的提线穿过它就好像是白熊正坐在冰面上钓鱼一样。这个可爱的杯盖适用于直径在 8 到 10 厘米的杯子，这是它的<a href=\"http://necktie.onlinestores.jp/category/select/pid/8765\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711212502kpPXU78IR6juGb1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711212502qxA5d8Mim1eDjY3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607112125024OqApLW5avnXdTRY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711212504YZdUy01RQgvjPJmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}